{"tid":686164,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"SUPPLY & DEMAND理論? 人仔成日入香港買野, 點解港元都係低水咁多?","createTime":"2018-06-01T04:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T07:22:34.000Z","uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd980d8f323fadb3b9b10f693d030c25a0bb1c9","tid":686164,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:20:11.000Z","msg":"成日講佢地一炮過買樓, 家下D樓都成千萬一間, 年年黃金週都唔會搶港紙搶到高水左.<br />\n<br />\n一年8千萬人黎香港, 港元匯價都係偏低, 港股升到3萬點, 成日講北水流入都影響唔到港元匯價, 係咩因由? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fd36dd0745316dd6b6d0baa891a3c3e17bad3d","tid":686164,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1a3e01bf01b5cde3487261f980323269608decf","tid":686164,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec203233be8e62db025e88cd9470d677e77f5866","tid":686164,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e1a3e01bf01b5cde3487261f980323269608decf","tid":686164,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:28:06.000Z","msg":"淘寶都係1百幾十, 黎香港買樓買股都係以百萬計, 差好遠喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49466fede8992ef82c707a99eed92cd79efab11b","tid":686164,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84fd36dd0745316dd6b6d0baa891a3c3e17bad3d","tid":686164,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"行入車箱自己摺埋啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3685d1d31d447addc9e04209198e34b5541de446","tid":686164,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:30:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc6c6c36c5da34ea57ef0e5fab5b2ab4d5