 />\n咁即係如果市場無咁多港紙去換返資產, 即係港爆? 一係要印多D港元, 一係就要跌匯率? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ed74afa3d65cf5d394fd1d15a042a5ffc22aee","tid":686164,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc6c6c36c5da34ea57ef0e5fab5b2ab4d503f848","tid":686164,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3685d1d31d447addc9e04209198e34b5541de446","tid":686164,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec203233be8e62db025e88cd9470d677e77f5866","tid":686164,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:28:06.000Z","msg":"淘寶都係1百幾十, 黎香港買樓買股都係以百萬計, 差好遠喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:30:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"股票D錢都日日落姐, 仲有自由行同水貨佬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:22:34.000Z","msg":"早兩年每日都接美金啲錢俾你食左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}